      "title": "Buenos Aires Argentina Temple",
      "score": 0.0898739463811358,
      "text": "Buenos Aires Argentina Temple\nThe Buenos Aires Argentina Temple is the 39th operating temple of The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints (LDS Church), located in Ciudad Evita, near Buenos Aires, Argentina.",
      "score_breakdown": {
        "dense": 0.049946517722715945,
