      "title": "Sportivo Italiano",
      "score": 0.04067537334044642,
      "text": "Sportivo Italiano\nClub Sportivo Italiano is an Argentine football club located in Ciudad Evita, La Matanza Partido, Greater Buenos Aires. The team currently plays in the Primera B Metropolitana, the third division of the Argentine football league system.",
