      "score": 0.04037530970873471,
      "text": "Ciudad del Niño metro station\nCiudad del Niño is an underground metro station on the Line 2 of the Santiago Metro, in Santiago, Chile. It is named for the former Ciudad del Niño Presidente Juan Antonio Ríos.",
      "score_breakdown": {
